values:
Dim just in one of those moods... today i was driving, and those of you who know me best know that i think&nbsp; a lot when i drive.&nbsp; i really wish that i could read peoples thoughts.&nbsp; i feel like the biggest bother to a lot of people, so i want to back off, but im not much of an alone type person any more.&nbsp; i cant be okay by myself.&nbsp; so i know that it would probably hurt to hear what people are thinking, but at least id know.&nbsp; and i could react.&nbsp; i could protect myself.&nbsp; im getting to the point where ive worried so much about making other people happy that now its almost too late for me.&nbsp; im entirely happy with things right now, but the way ive brought it on means that i could lose it all in a second.&nbsp; its almost inevitable;&nbsp; but im going to be blind sided by it.&nbsp; im afraid that when i go to china with no contact back here for three weeks that ill be forgotten by a few people.&nbsp; i just have to keep telling myself that those are the people who didnt mean much in my life anyway.&nbsp; i could never forget someone after three weeks, but most people leave an impact on me whether its good or bad.. and i cant just get rid of that.&nbsp; i hate to think that ive made myself so disposable, but thats what ive set up for myself.&nbsp; i guess i screwed myself over in that respect.&nbsp; i really have no clue what im saying or if it makes sense.. im just trying to make sense of everything in my head.&nbsp; i guess it helped though.. i figured out what is bothering me.&nbsp; i really do feel disposable..&nbsp;

on another note, i have a chance to change that.&nbsp; but im too big of a wuss that i dont know if im going to be able to.. i have about 1 hour and 20 minutes to get it done on tuesday.. will i be able to???&nbsp; my roommate said i might as well.. shes right too.&nbsp; well see :-)

i dont know what else to put right now...
